WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.140
 

00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:17.590
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:00:17.590 --> 00:00:24.160
WOW. WOW.

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:27.130
I AM A MAN. I AM A NATION.

00:00:27.130 --> 00:00:31.870
LOCK INTO MY FREQUENCY. TUNE INTO MY STATION.

00:00:31.870 --> 00:00:35.610
SIT UP IN YOUR CHAIR, GRAB A DRINK FROM THE FRIDGE.

00:00:35.610 --> 00:00:37.540
WE NEED TO HAVE A CONVERSATION.

00:00:37.540 --> 00:00:40.310
COME MEET ME ON THE BRIDGE.

00:00:40.310 --> 00:00:44.320
SO, HERE I AM ONSTAGE AT UCLA,

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:47.290
