00:03:23.610 --> 00:03:24.910
AND NOW I'M SITTING AT THE CHURCH

00:03:24.910 --> 00:03:26.840
WITH THE NICEST MAN IN THE WORLD.

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:30.550
