00:03:30.550 --> 00:03:32.820
HE SMILES AT EVERYTHING.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:34.220
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:03:34.220 --> 00:03:36.820
NO, FOR REAL. IF YOU PUT HIM IN A HORROR MOVIE,

00:03:36.820 --> 00:03:40.160
HE WOULD STILL SMILE.

00:03:40.160 --> 00:03:42.060
YOU PUT HIM IN "FRIDAY THE 13th,"

00:03:42.060 --> 00:03:43.700
