00:03:43.700 --> 00:03:46.900
HA, HA, HA, HA! CHH, CHH, CHH! HA!"

00:03:46.900 --> 00:03:47.930
PASTER JOEL WOULD WALK UP.

00:03:47.930 --> 00:03:51.170
"WELL, JASON, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:03:51.170 --> 00:03:53.300
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO STAB PEOPLE.

00:03:53.300 --> 00:03:55.440
