00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:20.800
PEOPLE WERE SHOCKED -- SHOCKED!

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:22.500
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:04:22.500 --> 00:04:25.470
WHEW! "WHAT'S HAPPENING TO OUR NATION?"

