"SAY SOMETHING ELSE! SAY SOMETHING ELSE!

00:04:56.200 --> 00:04:58.670
DON'T MAKE ME -- OOH, OOH! SAY SOMETHING ELSE.

00:04:58.670 --> 00:05:02.410
I WILL COME ACROSS THIS BRIDGE. I WILL BUST YOU IN YOUR EYE!"

00:05:02.410 --> 00:05:04.010
[ LAUGHTER ]

