00:05:06.610 --> 00:05:08.380
COME ON 'ROUND HERE. COME ON 'ROUND HERE.

00:05:08.380 --> 00:05:09.980
RIGHT 'BOUT RIGHT THERE. COME ON.

00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:12.020
I GOT MY CONCEAL/CARRY. COME ON, BOY.

00:05:12.020 --> 00:05:15.320
COME OOOOOOOON! COME ON! COME ON!

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:16.790
COME ON!"

00:05:16.790 --> 00:05:24.000
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.960
THE BRIDGE.

00:05:25.960 --> 00:05:28.830
[ LAUGHTER ]

