[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:05:41.580 --> 00:05:45.080
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:49.420
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:05:49.420 --> 00:05:51.520
WE DON'T GET A CHANCE TO INVALIDATE SOMEBODY,

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:52.890
BECAUSE WE DON'T UNDERSTAND

00:05:52.890 --> 00:05:55.590
HOW THEY GOT TO A CERTAIN CONCLUSION.

00:05:55.590 --> 00:05:57.500
WE'VE GOT TO LEARN HOW TO HEAL.

00:05:57.500 --> 00:05:59.700
WE'VE GOT TO LEARN HOW TO DEAL.

00:05:59.700 --> 00:06:03.040
AND SO I CAN'T STAY IN THESE POLARIC PLACES,

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:07.070
WHETHER I'M FAR LEFT OR FAR RIGHT.

00:06:07.070 --> 00:06:09.280
SOMEHOW, I GOT TO GET US TO THE MIDDLE.

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:10.680
SOMEBODY SAY "MEET ME IN THE MIDDLE."

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:12.180
-MEET ME IN THE MIDDLE! -MEET ME IN THE MIDDLE!

00:06:12.180 --> 00:06:13.710
SEE, THIS IS THE KEY.

00:06:13.710 --> 00:06:16.410
