[ BEATBOXING ]

00:06:39.770 --> 00:06:42.580
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:06:42.580 --> 00:06:45.210
Y'ALL BETTER GO AHEAD. Y'ALL ARE LIKE,

