"THIS IS WONDERFUL. I'VE NEVER DONE THIS.

00:06:48.110 --> 00:06:49.920
THIS IS AMAZING.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:52.780
IS THIS WHAT THEY DO, AND THEY BACK IT UP?

00:06:52.780 --> 00:06:57.360
I WANT TO BACK IT UP! I WANT TO BACK IT UP."

