AND WHEN I WAS GROWING UP,

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:48.480
THE IDEA OF MORALITY AND RELATIONSHIP

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:50.450
AND SPIRITUALITY WERE ALL INTERWOVEN.

00:11:50.450 --> 00:11:51.780
WHEN I WAS 13, MY MOTHER WAS LIKE,

00:11:51.780 --> 00:11:53.520
"YOU'RE GONNA BE A VIRGIN WHEN YOU GET MARRIED."

