[ LAUGHTER ]

00:11:54.890 --> 00:11:56.450
SOMEBODY'S LAUGHING. I'M LIKE,

00:11:56.450 --> 00:11:58.320
"LISTEN, FIRST OF ALL, MOM,

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:02.030
I'VE GOT BUCKTEETH FROM SUCKING MY THUMB ALL OF MY CHILDHOOD,

00:12:02.030 --> 00:12:03.830
AND I'VE GOT BALD SPOTS FROM ALOPECIA.

00:12:03.830 --> 00:12:06.000
I DON'T THINK YOU NEED TO WORRY."

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:08.370
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:12:08.370 --> 00:12:09.600
IT'S ONE THING TO LIVE HOLY.

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:11.940
IT'S ANOTHER WHEN YOU DON'T HAVE OPTIONS.

00:12:11.940 --> 00:12:15.340
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:12:15.340 --> 00:12:17.580
SEE SOMEBODY TALKING ABOUT, "I'M WAITING ON THE LORD."

00:12:17.580 --> 00:12:19.110
I BET YOU ARE.

00:12:19.110 --> 00:12:21.980
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:12:21.980 --> 00:12:25.620
MM-HMM!

00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:29.820
[ LAUGHS ]

00:12:29.820 --> 00:12:31.720
WHEN I THINK ABOUT THE BRIDGE,

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:35.190
I THINK ABOUT WHAT IT IS I MUST DO TO CONNECT

00:12:35.190 --> 00:12:38.030
AND ENGAGE PEOPLE THAT DIDN'T COME FROM WHERE I COME FROM

00:12:38.030 --> 00:12:40.570
SO THAT WE CAN HAVE A PLACE OF COMMONALITY AND UNDERSTANDING.

00:12:40.570 --> 00:12:41.870
I'M NOT TALKING ABOUT CONVERSION,

00:12:41.870 --> 00:12:43.070
BECAUSE FOR TOO LONG,

00:12:43.070 --> 00:12:45.300
IN CERTAIN AREAS OF CHRISTIAN THOUGHT,

00:12:45.300 --> 00:12:48.740
WE HAVE TRIED TO SHAME PEOPLE INTO CHANGING.

00:12:48.740 --> 00:12:52.240
[ SCATTERED CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:54.280
WHAT'S FUNNY IS IT'S NOT JUST RELIGIOUS THOUGHT,

00:12:54.280 --> 00:12:56.050
BECAUSE EVEN IN POLITICAL IDEOLOGY,

00:12:56.050 --> 00:13:01.920
THIS IS THE FIRST POLITICAL CYCLE

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:07.060
WHERE OUR ELECTION WAS A RESULT OF SHAME,

00:13:07.060 --> 00:13:11.160
WHERE PEOPLE WHO WERE SHAMED FOR HAVING A PARTICULAR IDEA

00:13:11.160 --> 00:13:12.870
ABOUT WHAT MATTERED TO THEM,

00:13:12.870 --> 00:13:15.830
AND THE ONLY RECOURSE THEY HAD WAS TO GO INTO

00:13:15.830 --> 00:13:18.570
AN ANONYMOUS BOOTH AND PICK SOMETHING

00:13:18.570 --> 00:13:21.910
THAT WAS MOST NOT LIKE WHAT MOST OF US THOUGHT WOULD COME OUT.

00:13:21.910 --> 00:13:23.240
AND HOW DID THAT HAPPEN?

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:25.440
BECAUSE SHAME HAS PERMEATED THE CULTURE,

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:28.050
AND IF YOU DON'T BELIEVE WHAT I BELIEVE, THEN SHAME ON YOU.

00:13:28.050 --> 00:13:30.620
AND IF YOU DON'T LIKE WHAT I LIKE, THEN SHAME ON YOU.

00:13:30.620 --> 00:13:34.090
AND SHAME HAS PERMEATED THE CULTURE, AND THE BRIDGE SAYS,

00:13:34.090 --> 00:13:36.660
"I DON'T UNDERSTAND YOU, I DON'T AGREE WITH YOU,

00:13:36.660 --> 00:13:38.260
AND WE MAY NEVER SEE EYE-TO-EYE,

00:13:38.260 --> 00:13:40.330
BUT IF WE'RE ALL IN THE SAME SPACE,

00:13:40.330 --> 00:13:43.360
AT LEAST WE CAN BEGIN THE DIALOGUE AND CONVERSATION

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.860
THAT MAY LEAD TO HEALING."

00:13:45.860 --> 00:13:53.370
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:13:53.370 --> 00:13:57.780
FOR ME, THERE'S THIS STORY IN THE BIBLE THAT I LOVE,

00:13:57.780 --> 00:14:00.180
BECAUSE, YOU KNOW, A LOT OF TIMES PEOPLE --

00:14:00.180 --> 00:14:01.480
WHEN I TELL THEM I'M A PREACHER, THEY'RE LIKE,

00:14:01.480 --> 00:14:03.550
"OH, HERE HE GOES. HE'S ABOUT TO JUDGE ME."

00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:06.720
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:11.460
I'M LIKE, "NO. I'M NOT THAT KIND OF GUY. JUST LET ME TALK!"

00:14:11.460 --> 00:14:15.290
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:14:15.290 --> 00:14:19.300
BUT I KNOW, BECAUSE SOME OF YOU HAVE SEEN BAD TV, BAD CHURCH TV

00:14:19.300 --> 00:14:20.900
LATE AT NIGHT, AND YOU SEE THE GUY ON THERE TALKING ABOUT,

00:14:20.900 --> 00:14:22.800
"I'M GONNA TELL YOU RIGHT NOW YOU BETTER CALL THAT NUMBER

00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:24.840
ON THE SCREEN RIGHT NOW, 'CAUSE IF YOU DON'T,

00:14:24.840 --> 00:14:26.940
YOU'RE GONNA BURN IN A HOT LAKE OF FIRE!

00:14:26.940 --> 00:14:29.380
I'M GONNA TELL YOU THAT RIGHT NOW!"

00:14:29.380 --> 00:14:30.610
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:14:30.610 --> 00:14:34.410
SIR, YOU'RE FRIGHTENING THE CHILDREN.

00:14:34.410 --> 00:14:37.650
BUT EVERY TIME I SEE JESUS IN THE NEW TESTAMENT,

00:14:37.650 --> 00:14:40.790
I SEE HIM ENCOUNTERING THE MOST BROKEN OF SOCIETY,

00:14:40.790 --> 00:14:42.120
AND THEY WERE ATTRACTED TO HIM.

00:14:42.120 --> 00:14:44.490
HOW IS THAT THE LEPERS AND THE LAME

00:14:44.490 --> 00:14:45.890
AND THE BROKEN AND THE DRUNKS

00:14:45.890 --> 00:14:48.830
AND THE PROSTITUTES THOUGHT HE WAS AMAZING?

00:14:48.830 --> 00:14:50.930
HOW IS IT THAT HE CONNECTED TO BROKEN PEOPLE,

00:14:50.930 --> 00:14:52.400
BUT THE PRIDEFUL, THE SPIRITUAL,

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:54.870
THE RELIGIOUS ELITE DIDN'T WANT TO HAVE ANYTHING TO DO WITH HIM?

00:14:54.870 --> 00:14:57.030
I SAID, "THAT'S THE KIND OF PERSON I'D WANT TO BE,

00:14:57.030 --> 00:14:59.200
THAT I CONNECT TO PEOPLE NO MATTER WHERE THEY ARE,

00:14:59.200 --> 00:15:00.640
NO MATTER WHAT THEY'RE DEALING WITH,

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:02.970
NO MATTER WHAT THEY LOOK LIKE." AND THAT'S NOT RELIGIOUS.

00:15:02.970 --> 00:15:05.580
THAT'S SEEING THE BEAUTY AND THE DIVINE NATURE

00:15:05.580 --> 00:15:08.950
OF EVERY HUMAN BEING THAT YOU ENCOUNTER.

00:15:08.950 --> 00:15:15.190
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:15:15.190 --> 00:15:17.690
THERE'S NOTHING MORE AMAZING TO ME THAN THIS STORY IN JOHN 4.

00:15:17.690 --> 00:15:19.760
JESUS IS TALKING TO THIS SAMARITAN WOMAN,

00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:21.630
AND JEWS AND SAMARITANS DID NOT HANG OUT.

00:15:21.630 --> 00:15:23.060
THEY WERE NOT BEDFELLOWS.

00:15:23.060 --> 00:15:25.260
JEWS KIND OF THOUGHT THEY WERE BETTER THAN THE SAMARITANS.

00:15:25.260 --> 00:15:27.200
SAMARITANS WAS KIND OF SLIGHTLY HOOD.

00:15:27.200 --> 00:15:29.640
THEY WAS LIKE, "WHATEVER, WHATEVER. WOOPTY-WOO."

00:15:29.640 --> 00:15:32.740
AND THE JEWS WERE LIKE, "UGH, UGH! EH!"

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:34.110
THAT WAS KIND OF THE VIBE.

00:15:34.110 --> 00:15:36.480
AND JEWS AND SAMARITANS DIDN'T REALLY TALK,

00:15:36.480 --> 00:15:37.880
YOU KNOW, TO ONE ANOTHER.

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:40.580
AND, SO, THIS SAMARITAN WOMAN IS WALKING UP,

00:15:40.580 --> 00:15:42.310
AND JESUS IS AT THE WELL.

00:15:42.310 --> 00:15:44.350
AND THEY'RE NOT EVEN SUPPOSED TO BE HAVING CONVERSATION.

00:15:44.350 --> 00:15:45.980
AND JESUS IS JUST CHILLIN' BY THE WELL.

00:15:45.980 --> 00:15:47.290
AND, YOU KNOW, IN ALL OF THE MOVIES,

00:15:47.290 --> 00:15:50.660
JESUS HAS A BRITISH ACCENT, EVEN THOUGH HE LIVED,

00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:53.560
YOU KNOW, IN ISRAEL 2,000 YEARS AGO, BUT WHATEVER.

00:15:53.560 --> 00:15:56.260
AND, SO, HE'S ALWAYS LIKE --

00:15:56.260 --> 00:15:58.860
HE ALWAYS HAS HIS JESUS BEARD WITH HIS PREMIUM BROWN SANDALS.

00:15:58.860 --> 00:16:00.360
AND HE'S SITTING BY THE WELL AND HE'S LIKE,

00:16:00.360 --> 00:16:02.930
"GIVE ME A DRRRINK OF WATER."

00:16:02.930 --> 00:16:04.500
AND, SO, I NEED YOU TO UNDERSTAND

00:16:04.500 --> 00:16:06.610
THE CULTURAL CONTEXT OF BUILDING BRIDGES,

00:16:06.610 --> 00:16:09.780
BECAUSE JESUS BUILT A BRIDGE WITH THIS LADY

00:16:09.780 --> 00:16:11.110
THAT DIDN'T COME FROM WHERE HE COME FROM

00:16:11.110 --> 00:16:12.510
AND DIDN'T BELIEVE WHAT HE BELIEVED.

00:16:12.510 --> 00:16:14.580
AND HE SAID, "HEY, CAN YOU GIVE ME A DRINK OF WATER?"

00:16:14.580 --> 00:16:17.080
AND SHE WAS FROM SAMARIA, SO SHE WAS A LITTLE BIT HOOD.

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:19.320
SHE WAS LIKE, "FIRST OF ALL, YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW ME,

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:21.690
SO WHY ARE YOU EVEN TALKING TO ME, OKAY?

00:16:21.690 --> 00:16:23.490
BECAUSE I'M A SAMARITAN.

00:16:23.490 --> 00:16:25.490
SAMARITANS, REPRESENT.

00:16:25.490 --> 00:16:29.800
ENH, ENH, ENH, ENH, ENH, ENH

00:16:29.800 --> 00:16:31.860
YOU NEED TO BACK UP, OKAY?

00:16:31.860 --> 00:16:34.300
'CAUSE YOU DON'T KNOW -- YOU DON'T KNOW ME!"

00:16:34.300 --> 00:16:36.900
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:16:36.900 --> 00:16:39.510
JESUS WAS LIKE, "IF YOU KNEW THE GIFT OF GOD

00:16:39.510 --> 00:16:42.070
AND WHO IT WAS THAT WAS STANDING HERE,

00:16:42.070 --> 00:16:43.480
YOU WOULD GIVE HIM A DRINK OF WATER

00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:45.610
AND YOU'D NEVER THIRST AGAIN!"

00:16:45.610 --> 00:16:48.050
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:16:48.050 --> 00:16:51.820
SHE WAS LIKE, "OH, MY GOODNESS.

00:16:51.820 --> 00:16:53.620
TELL ME ABOUT THIS WATER. WHERE IS THIS WATER?

00:16:53.620 --> 00:16:57.050
I'VE BEEN THIRSTY FOR A LONG TIME, OKAY?

00:16:57.050 --> 00:16:59.620
FOR REAL, FOR REAL."

00:16:59.620 --> 00:17:03.700
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:17:03.700 --> 00:17:05.400
YOU GOT TO READ IT. SOME OF YOU ARE LIKE,

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:08.670
"I DIDN'T READ THAT IN..." IT'S IN THE N.I.V.,

00:17:08.670 --> 00:17:10.370
THE NEGRO INTERNATIONAL VERSION.

00:17:10.370 --> 00:17:14.440
