00:17:24.520 --> 00:17:26.680
BUT WHY DON'T YOU GO GET YOUR HUSBAND FIRST."

00:17:26.680 --> 00:17:30.560
SHE WAS LIKE, "MNH, WELL, JUST SO YOU KNOW, I'M SINGLE, OKAY?

00:17:30.560 --> 00:17:32.690
