00:17:32.690 --> 00:17:34.430
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:17:34.430 --> 00:17:35.960
HE WAS LIKE, "SLOW DOWN, BOO. I'M GONNA SAVE Y'ALL.

00:17:35.960 --> 00:17:40.060
I DON'T EVEN GET DOWN LIKE THAT, ALL RIGHT? JUST RELAX."

00:17:40.060 --> 00:17:42.530
SO, THEN JESUS TAKES THIS REAL REGULAR CONVERSATION

00:17:42.530 --> 00:17:43.940
