00:17:50.710 --> 00:17:52.140
SHE WAS LIKE, "FIRST OF ALL, HOLD ON.

00:17:52.140 --> 00:17:53.910
WHO TOLD YOU MY BUSINESS?

00:17:53.910 --> 00:17:56.650
SHANIQUA! SHANIQUA, DID YOU TELL THIS MAN MY BUSINESS?

00:17:56.650 --> 00:17:58.450
I TOLD YOU TO BE QUIET!"

00:17:58.450 --> 00:18:02.920
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:18:02.920 --> 00:18:05.520
Y'ALL DIDN'T KNOW SHANIQUA WAS IN THE BIBLE TILL YOU MET ME.

00:18:05.520 --> 00:18:06.620
SEE?

00:18:06.620 --> 00:18:09.160
SuperSoul SESSIONS.

00:18:09.160 --> 00:18:12.630
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:18:12.630 --> 00:18:14.630
IT'S IN THE SESSION.

00:18:14.630 --> 00:18:20.570
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:18:20.570 --> 00:18:24.840
