BECAUSE WE DON'T AGREE.

00:19:35.650 --> 00:19:38.080
I'M TALKING ABOUT A LOVE THAT MAKES ME FIGHT FOR YOU,

00:19:38.080 --> 00:19:40.280
EVEN THOUGH I DON'T SEE WHAT YOU SEE.

00:19:40.280 --> 00:19:42.950
I'M TALKING ABOUT A LOVE THAT MAKES ME CROSS THE BRIDGE

00:19:42.950 --> 00:19:45.760
OF UNDERSTANDING, AWAY FROM MY FEARFUL PLACE.

00:19:45.760 --> 00:19:50.860
I'M TALKING ABOUT A BRIDGE THAT MAKES ME SEE YOU FACE-TO-FACE.

00:19:50.860 --> 00:19:53.030
-YEAH! -MM-HMM!

00:19:53.030 --> 00:19:57.100
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:19:57.100 --> 00:19:59.640
-PREACH! -I'M TRYING, GIRL.

00:19:59.640 --> 00:20:02.210
[ LAUGHTER ]

