00:21:11.210 --> 00:21:14.310
[ CROWD MURMURS ]

00:21:14.310 --> 00:21:16.110
BECAUSE IF YOU'RE GONNA BUILD BRIDGES,

00:21:16.110 --> 00:21:17.550
YOU'RE GONNA CONNECT WITH PEOPLE

00:21:17.550 --> 00:21:20.290
AND HAVE TO CONNECT WITH PEOPLE THAT DON'T LOOK LIKE YOU,

00:21:20.290 --> 00:21:22.650
DON'T LIVE WHERE YOU LIVE.

